# Herminox — daily plan & hard rules

## Security 10/10 (never violate)
- No Telegram/Discord scraping, cold DMs, NLP from private chats
- No Reddit/forum spam bots
- No thin 10k PSEO; no Seller Central phishing; no storing calculator inputs on servers
- Prefill query URLs are for humans only (`noindex`); index only clean unique URLs

## Safe growth stack (do these)
1. Prefill deep-links (done for FBA + ACoS; extend others)
2. Embed widgets + manual coach/blogger outreach
3. Quality long-tail `/guides/` — **3–5 unique pages/day** (formula + table + example each)
4. GSC: sitemap, indexing, Core Web Vitals
5. Public read-only Calc API — later
6. Manual helpful Reddit/forum answers — no bots

